    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Driven Pulley pressure measurement"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Assemble the A/T oil pressure hose (07MAJ-PY40110) and joint (07MAJ-PY40120) to the pressure gauge set 16000 kPa (07YAJ-0010410) and install it in the driven pulley pressure detection hole (A)."
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "Driven Pulley pressure measurement requires a measurement pressure of 5,000 kPa (51.0 kgf/cm). 2 The pressure gauge set of 16000 kPa must be used because the pressure may be higher than 16000 kPa."
      ]
    },
